What does your company do?
Wormsensing develops and commercializes the world’s most sensitive and compact piezoceramic sensors to monitor vibration and deformation in real time. Our flagship product, Dragonfly®, enables unprecedented insight into the mechanical behavior of machines — from aerospace engines to manufacturing lines. Thanks to its ultra-thin format, plug & play design, and extreme sensitivity (1000× over legacy sensors), Dragonfly® captures what traditional sensors miss: subtle deformation signals at the source, even on moving or embedded parts. With over 40 patents, strong traction (+110% YoY), and a proven in-house production capacity (2M units/year), Wormsensing bridges physical performance with digital intelligence — for a safer, smarter, more efficient industry.
